# .trivyignore

# CVEs suppressed here must have a written justification.

# Review this file on every dependency upgrade.

# Format: CVE-YYYY-NNNNN # reason; expires: YYYY-MM-DD

# CVE-2026-6270 (@fastify/middie authentication bypass in child plugin scopes)

# Fixed in @fastify/middie 9.3.2 which requires Fastify 5.

# @nestjs/platform-fastify@10 pins Fastify 4 — no compatible fix available.

# NOT exploitable in this service: we use no child plugin scopes with

# authentication middleware. All routes are protected by NestJS guards at

# the controller layer, not Fastify middleware. Revisit when upgrading to

# NestJS 11 + Fastify 5.

# expires: 2026-12-31

CVE-2026-6270
